---
import render from "../../../assets/images/AsphaltPlant/render.webp";
import bg1 from "../../../assets/images/About/Delivery/hero2.webp";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
---

<section class="w-full mt-20 lg:mt-32 flex flex-col gap-10">
    <div
        class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 lg:px-52 flex items-center justify-center"
    >
        <h1 class="text-grisT font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-center">
            ADVANTAGES
        </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-blueMain text-center font-bold text-2xl lg:text-3xl">
            Design and fabrication under the highest quality standards to ensure
            continuous hot-mix production with minimal breakdowns
        </h2>
    </div><br />
    <div
        class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 text-lg lg:text-xl"
    >
        <div>
            <p class="text-center">
                Extra-reinforced drum chassis designed to maintain perfect
                alignment of the drum bearing system, minimizing wear on
                bearings, trunnions, and steel tires.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p class="text-center">
                Design and fabrication refined to the last detail, backed by the
                experience of over 300 asphalt plants manufactured and
                continuously improved through the maintenance services we
                provide.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class=" flex justify-center max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <Image src={render} alt="" />
    </div>
    <div
        class="relative w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center min-h-[50vh] px-8 py-10 bg-cover bg-[center_bottom] bg-no-repeat"
        style={{
            backgroundImage: `url(${bg1.src})`,
        }}
    >
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1f3c66]/70"></div>

        <h1 class=" relative font-bold text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-center text-white">
            Mobility and Installation
        </h1><br />
        <div
            class=" relative w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto text-white grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 py-10 text-lg lg:text-xl"
        >
            <div>
                <p class="text-center">
                    Compact and mobile size, perfect for short-term jobs with
                    frequent relocations.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="text-center">
                    Simple installation and leveling of the equipment—mixing
                    drum, bins unit, and asphalt tank—thanks to predetermined
                    chassis height and alignment.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto py-10">
        <h1 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-black text-center">
            Material Handling
        </h1><br />
        <div
            class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 px-8 py-10 font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl text-redBg text-center"
        >
            <div>
                <p>High capacity bins that reduce payloader dependency.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    Dosing and feeding conveyor systems manufactured under CEMA
                    standards
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-black">
            Asphalt and Fuel Systems
        </h3>
        <div
            class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 py-10 font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl text-blueMain text-justify"
        >
            <div>
                <p>
                    Asphalt injection pump submerged inside the asphalt tank,
                    eliminating the need to purge and pre-heat the jacket
                    system; immediate startup, even in the coldest climates.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    Fuel filtering system designed for burning waste oils,
                    preventing clogged fuel lines. <br /><br />
                    Fuel filtering system, pre-heater, and fuel pump mounted on a
                    hinged and sliding base, keeping the pump at a low level to avoid
                    purging and starting issues.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
